      "text": "Un apmettahs pretti teem/\\nn pohstija tahs Semmes Dru-\\nwes/ ka nahk us Gazu/ un ne at-\\nlizzinaja ne kahdu Mifchannu eekſch\\nIsraëta/neds tihkus Lohpus/neds\\nWehrschus/ nedś Ehsetus.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 5,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Jo tee nahze ar jaweem Ban-\\nnama-Pulkeem un ar jaweem\\nDsihwolkeem us angfchu/ tee\\nnahze itt ka Siffeni pulkā/ ka tohs\\nar jaweem Kanre-teem ne warreja\\nsknitibt/ un tee nahze tai Semmē\\nwixau pohstiht.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 6,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tad isginne Israëls fohti\\nto Midijaniteu deht. Tad brehze\\nIṣraëta Behrni us to KUNGU.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 7,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un kad Israëta Behrni us\\nto KUNGU brehze to Midijanite-\\nen deht/\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 8,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tad fuhtija tas KUNGS\\nweenu Wihru/ kas Praueets bi-\\nja pee Israëta Behrneem/ tas\\nfazzija us winneem: ta fakka tas\\nKUNGS Israëta Deews: Es\\nefmu juhs no Egiptes isweddis/\\nun juhs no to Wahrgu-Namma\\nisweddis/\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 9,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un efinu juhs isglahbis no\\nto Egipteru Rohkas/ un no wit\\nfu Rohkas/ kas juhs speede/ un\\nefinn tohs juhsu Preetſcha tsdsin-\\nnis/ un juhs winnu Semmi De-\\nwis.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 10,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un es fazziju us jums: Es\\nefinu tas KUNgs juhsu Deews/\\nne bihstreetees to Amoriteu Dee-\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 11,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tad nahze ta KUNGA\\nEngelis/ un apsehdehs appakſch\\nto Ohsola/ kas Owra irr/ kas Jo-\\nasam Esrus Tehwam peederrja/\\nun winna Dehs Gideans kuhte\\nKweeschus pee ta Wihna-Spai-\\nda/ ka wiꞥſch behgdams to ats-\\nwestu/ preekſch teem Midijanite-\\nteem.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 12,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tad rahdijahs winnam\\nta KUNGA Engelis/ un fazzija\\nus winnu: Tas KUNGS irr ar\\ntew/ tu stiprs un firdigs Wihrs.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 13,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Bet Gideans fazzija us\\nwinnu: Ak mans Kungs/ kad\\ntas KUNGS ar mums irr/\\nkapetz tad wiffas tchihs Leetas\\nmums irr usgabjutchas? un kur\\nirr wiꞥſt winna Brihnuni/ ko\\nmums muhsa Tehwi irr teikun-\\nkht/ fazzidami: Neggi tas\\nKUNGS muhs no Egiptes irr\\nisweddis? bet nu irr tas KUNgs\\nmuhs atstahjis/ un to Midtjani-\\nteru Rohkā dewis.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 14,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tad atgreejahsts Kungs\\nus winnu/ un fazzija: No-cij\\nschinui tanā Spehā/ jo few\\nbuhs Israëlu atpestiht no to Mi-\\ndijaniteu Rohkas/ reds/ Es tew\\nesinu fuhtijs.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 15,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un wiꞥſch fazzija us to:\\nmans Kungs/ ar ko atpesti-\\nchn es Israëlu/ rangi mannu\\nRaddu Puks ter tas rettakajs\\neekſch Manassus/ un es efinu tas\\nmasakajs manna Tehwa Nainā.\n"
    }
